title: You Choose 9: Extreme Machine Challenge
description: "YOU CHOOSE . . . Daredevil driver or kidnapping by super spies! You are attending the Extreme Machine Expo. Every type of fast car is on display u some are even available to test! Among the mind-boggling collection of sports cars, hovercrafts and jet planes are strange characters. Could they be secret agents? Will you become a pro racer, or will the machines send you spinning out of control?"
